tags: Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: A very sound doctor who gives the patient time and explains everything with clarity and precision. Appointments with her in her chembur clinic are very accessible and with minimal waiting time. I highly recommend her for patients in and around chembur.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
context: Pre and Post Delivery Care,Cesarean Delivery,
review: Very genuine, punctual and supportive... Thank You so much Dr. For bringing my Bundle of Joy ðŸŽŠ safely in this world.

Good at her professional work.But she is not worried about the patients much.If asked for any immediate query,no response.We have to struggle to get her in call incase of any emergency need.Staff appointed does not have a decent approach.Doctor does not understands that its our first pregnancy and we need some extra piece of advise about foods or things to be practised.When asked for a second opinion she did not help me,though she knew I was going to deliver my baby at my hometown.If taken a little care for patients beyond her professionalism,it may help.

I found Dr. Gauri gore very rude, not friendly and unapproachable.
I was afraid to ask her my doubts and queries as she was answering my questions as if she was doing a favour on me and was making faces.
A doctor specially gynecologist shold be approachable so that patients should feel comfortable while asking their queries.
She charged me Rs. 600 for her 10 minuites of rudeness and it was definitely not worth.
I will not recommend her to any of my contacts.
Doctor is very punchual for time  and  has very efficiently done the treatment for  my wife. Overall very good  experience.

During 9 month of my pregnancy I was under her treatment. I was totally satisfied. I recommend  everyone  to consult Dr Gouri Gore for any gyne problem. But I would suggest madam to  be a little frank with her patients.

Overall Excellent Experience. She performed best for her patient's. Agreed that she is quit less talkative but keep transparency in her advise.

It is a worse than government hospital, the staff is worse. You have to wait for hours to wait despite taking appointment do not ever visit the hospital. No issues to doctor.. meet her in any other hospital for consultancy.
She is gentle,  caring.,  very patient and extremely confident.  Explains your illness which is very boosting.
